<p>Samuel Hawley &#8211; &#8220;The Imjin War&#8221;</p>
<p>Kenneth W. Swope &#8211; &#8220;A Dragon&#8217;s Head and a Serpent&#8217;s Tail&#8221;</p>
<p>Stephen Turnbull &#8211; &#8220;The Samurai Invasion of Korea&#8221;</p>
